# Feedback log

> Both **corrections** ("don't do X") and **confirmations** ("yes that's the right approach") are saved here. Confirmations are quieter signals — watch for them and record. Each entry includes *Why* (the reason given, often a past incident or strong preference) and *How to apply* (when/where the rule kicks in), so future-you can judge edge cases.

