## Conventions

- New feedback (correction or confirmation) MUST include *Why* and *How to apply*.
- If feedback turns out wrong / superseded, mark the entry as `STATUS: superseded by FB-NNN` rather than deleting.
- Feedback patterns recurring ≥3 times across sessions deserve promotion to `CLAUDE.md` operating constraints.
